title: Prudent Media Konkani Prime 30 October 13 Part 3
description: God of cricket, Sachin Tendulkar guided Mumbai to victory against Haryana, in the last domestic match of his glorious career. Sachin remained unbeaten on 79 runs to take his home team to the target against Haryana, on  a difficult pitch in Rohtak, on Wednesday morning.
